g.aria-label: while all is layed out on a large canvas
first, open File document properties and set document size to 160 x 90
the actual size is not important, we just want to set a proper aspect ratio of 16:9
second, install the jessyink script that's it!
and apply the order of appreance to each frame, starting with 0.
to hide or unhide objects, use the Effects Dialog
select the object and apply an order, to appear or disappear.
In the example "with Jessyink" is shown at step 3 and never disappears as out effect is set to type "none"
